        <figcaption>李家超在当选后，与妻子拥抱庆祝。（路透社）</figcaption></figure><figure class="image-placeholder "><img alt="" class="" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/2022-05/hong_kong-china-politics-050106.jpg?VersionId=GXcGuF6N4dcDy0oCMf5bXQzaCl0uPR_L" pinger-seen="true" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">
